{"tid":1209744,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"下午5點左右 信報記者狗於太古廣場影人相","createTime":"2019-06-12T12:12:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T12:56:08.000Z","uid":63667,"like":43,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"cf3eb5c4e39bf4e786b8fe593b3aaf26c98a17f1","tid":1209744,"uid":63667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T12:12:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QCAsAAY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQCAsAAY.png&h=ac9e3712&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n圖中為信報記者，全名：黃叔根<br />\n<br />\n今日於太古廣場時<br />\n圖中信報記者對未有口罩示威者拍照<br />\n被A女性發現後要求刪除照片<br />\n信報記者表示拒絕<br />\n<br />\n其後更多人圍住信報記者<br />\n要求其刪除照片<br />\n但記者繼續對周圍的人拍照<br />\n直至2,30人將其圍住<br />\n<br />\n期間該男子多次以嘻皮笑臉態度挑釁眾人<br />\n後來又反指A女性偷走其記憶卡<br />\n到太古廣場保安人員到後<br />\n又反口稱記憶卡已遺失<br />\n並要求報警處理<br />\n<br />\n本人因體力不支而先行離開<br />\n離開前亦為此記者拍照留念<br />\n若有在場人士有後續發展<br />\n歡迎補充<br />\n<br />\n本文以書面語所寫，為方便各位轉貼到國外。<br />\n<br />\n香港加油！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ec79e8bae8c9b86cb886b5470f157066db5ab3b","tid":1209744,"uid":63667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T12:14:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"11df3847f241ac95aa4f7049d7e2334d3b7a1bda","tid":1209744,"uid":171786,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T12:16:13.000Z","msg":"又會咁忍得冇人打柒佢嘅"},{"pid":"b4414eb574cb2d9bb84de52ea3dbb7b499855475","tid":1209744,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T12:16:42.000Z","msg":"火雲邪神"},{"pid":"be4fa8b4a684568f8b42481ace01202ea164d0bd","tid":1209744,"uid":63667,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"11df3847f241ac95aa4f7049d7e2334d3b7a1bda","tid":1209744,"uid":171786,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T12:16:13.000Z","msg":"又會咁忍得冇人打柒佢嘅"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T12:16:57.000Z","msg":"大家阻止左好幾位巴打<br />\n包括阻止左我"},{"pid":"c9f68d1982ebf3832fb61bbab924c8cd84ab0664","tid":1209744,"ui